   INTRODUCTION

'gtkcontour' is a graphical frontend that allow to construct a so-called apparent
contours; moreover it use the 'contour' program to verify if the graphic
obtained is or not a apparent contour. Refer to the 'contour' program
description for further informations.

   INSTALLATION

Compilation and installation are quite standard on a unix system,
with the usual chain of commands "./configure", "make", "make install";
we refer to the file INSTALL for details.

